        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A <em>guardian staff</em> is formed from ivory strands woven in a diamond pattern and capped with a glowing ruby. Those charged with protecting others value this staff's spells.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> envision</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You raise the staff and choose an ally within 10 feet. A ruby-colored plane of force appears like a shield near the ally, granting them a +1 circumstance bonus to AC until the start of your next turn. If you use this action again, any creature you previously granted this bonus to loses it.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Forbidding Ward]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Sanctuary]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spirit Link]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shield Other]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spirit Link]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
